WEBVTT

00:02.540 --> 00:06.630
<b><i>This little light
I've found</i></b>

00:08.750 --> 00:12.840
<b><i>Take it in,
breathe it out</i></b>

00:15.220 --> 00:19.260
<b><i>A little drum
that's beating loud</i></b>

00:21.640 --> 00:26.150
<b><i>In my chest,
I hear the sound</i></b>

00:31.320 --> 00:33.750
<b><i>I can feel</i></b>

00:33.750 --> 00:36.200
<b><i>Feel you now</i></b>

00:36.200 --> 00:39.160
<b><i>I can feel you now</i></b>

00:39.160 --> 00:41.830
<b><i>I can feel</i></b>

00:41.830 --> 00:45.370
<b><i>I can feel you now</i></b>

01:03.230 --> 01:06.470
<b>I don't think you understand
how much trouble you're in.</b>

01:09.860 --> 01:11.420
<b>Bodies are piling up</b>

01:11.420 --> 01:13.610
<b>and you appear to be in the middle of it.</b>

01:41.210 --> 01:43.250
<b>Our conversation will be recorded</b>

01:43.250 --> 01:46.190
<b>and handed over to the civilian 
police oversight commission.</b>

01:46.190 --> 01:48.600
<b>So it's in your best interest</b>

01:48.600 --> 01:51.640
<b>to answer my questions honestly 
and to the best of your ability.</b>

01:54.330 --> 01:55.860
<b>I can help you.</b>

01:56.520 --> 01:57.880
<b>If you'll let me.</b>

01:59.490 --> 02:03.290
<b>With all due respect, sir, 
this is a waste of time.</b>

02:03.290 --> 02:06.640
<b>Go read my case report. 
Everything I know is in there.</b>

02:08.000 --> 02:10.580
<b>The case report where you claimed the murders</b>

02:10.580 --> 02:13.350
<b>of Senator Bannister and 
Chief Grant were connected.</b>

02:16.130 --> 02:20.190
<b>And that we should be looking for 
a replicant called "Black Lotus."</b>

02:21.950 --> 02:25.580
<b>The police oversight commission got 
copies of your replicant theory.</b>

02:27.340 --> 02:30.400
<b>I sent my report to everyone up the chain.</b>

02:30.400 --> 02:32.240
<b>And no one wants to listen.</b>

02:38.860 --> 02:40.350
<b>This is investigator Alan Chen,</b>

02:41.260 --> 02:44.960
<b>interviewing subject 
Officer Alani Davis, LAPD.</b>

02:51.580 --> 02:52.840
<b>Let's begin.</b>

02:54.350 --> 02:58.230
<b>Officer Davis, what do you know about 
the one they're calling Black Lotus?</b>

02:58.950 --> 03:00.790
<b>I was one of the first officers on scene</b>

03:00.790 --> 03:03.440
<b>at the death of Senator Bannister.</b>

03:21.270 --> 03:25.470
<b>The Senator and his pals were regulars 
at underground replicant fights.</b>

03:25.470 --> 03:27.410
<b>But this night, he was alone.</b>

03:27.730 --> 03:30.770
<b><i>Confirmed. Personal bodyguard called it in.</i></b>

03:41.110 --> 03:43.090
<b>That's when I saw her.</b>

03:43.090 --> 03:45.020
<b>How did you know it was her?</b>

03:45.020 --> 03:47.050
<b>She looked a certain kind of nervous.</b>

03:47.570 --> 03:49.240
<b>But more than that.</b>

03:49.240 --> 03:50.930
<b>I'm with the police. Stop.</b>

03:51.870 --> 03:54.170
<b><i>Davis, where are you?</i></b>

03:54.740 --> 03:56.270
<b>I said stop!</b>

03:56.270 --> 03:58.570
<b>My instincts told me
something was wrong.</b>

03:58.570 --> 04:00.510
<b>Her identifying mark is 
a Black Lotus tattoo.</b>

04:00.510 --> 04:02.370
<b><i>Davis, acknowledge.</i></b>

04:08.920 --> 04:10.890
<b>According to his bodyguard,</b>

04:10.890 --> 04:14.010
<b>the Senator had plenty of political 
enemies that would want him dead.</b>

04:14.930 --> 04:16.740
<b>But on that night,</b>

04:16.740 --> 04:20.250
<b>the only thing the Senator was worried 
about was his missing journalist friend.</b>

04:22.160 --> 04:27.380
<b>The Senator's cause of death was 
asphyxiation due to a crushed windpipe.</b>

04:28.370 --> 04:32.540
<b>From the marks on his neck, the 
killer had replicant strength.</b>

04:34.600 --> 04:36.160
<b>Replicant strength?</b>

04:36.160 --> 04:38.100
<b>I trust my intuition.</b>

04:40.020 --> 04:43.430
<b>So what did your intuition lead to next?</b>

04:43.900 --> 04:46.520
<b>Not a lot of replicants left in this city.</b>

04:47.010 --> 04:49.060
<b>So I put my ear to the ground.</b>

04:54.920 --> 04:58.110
<b>My intel led me to a street 
gang in Silver Lake.</b>

05:01.380 --> 05:04.590
<b>Drove, I want to talk with you.</b>

05:07.510 --> 05:09.160
<b>You gotta be kidding.</b>

05:09.750 --> 05:12.330
<b>What do you want, little piggy?
You ain't got nothing on me.</b>

05:12.330 --> 05:14.000
<b>Whoa. Ow!</b>

05:14.000 --> 05:16.320
<b>Heard you had a run-in with a young woman.</b>

05:16.320 --> 05:19.280
<b>Bad attitude.
Tattoo of a Black Lotus.</b>

05:19.280 --> 05:22.440
<b>Why would I help a pretty, 
little piggy like you?</b>

05:22.440 --> 05:24.890
<b>Aah, jeez!
Okay, okay. Ow!</b>

05:37.320 --> 05:39.720
<b>Police business.
Now move along.</b>

05:40.260 --> 05:41.530
<b>To hell with this.</b>

05:45.330 --> 05:47.270
<b>She cut the boss up.</b>

05:47.580 --> 05:50.750
<b>She's nuts. Carried a damn samurai sword.</b>

05:59.760 --> 06:01.750
<b>You better give me more than that.</b>

06:01.750 --> 06:05.090
<b>All right. All right. You win.</b>

06:05.090 --> 06:06.520
<b>She had this tech.</b>

06:06.520 --> 06:07.840
<b>We tried to take it from her.</b>

06:07.840 --> 06:10.600
<b>We was just messing around.</b>

06:11.060 --> 06:13.010
<b>Then she comes back to kill us.</b>

06:13.010 --> 06:15.250
<b>Neuro-stims must've messed her brain up!</b>

06:20.560 --> 06:25.650
<b>A few days earlier, a woman with a 
Black Lotus tattoo and inhuman strength</b>

06:25.650 --> 06:27.660
<b>beat the crap out of the same gang.</b>

07:00.200 --> 07:01.980
<b>What the hell do you want?</b>

07:08.650 --> 07:10.260
<b>Go to hell.</b>

07:19.880 --> 07:22.640
<b>And she killed their leader.</b>

07:27.040 --> 07:28.970
<b>Consider the source.</b>

07:29.890 --> 07:32.620
<b>You can't take the testimony 
of a street gang seriously.</b>

07:33.100 --> 07:34.810
<b>Based on her behavior,</b>

07:34.810 --> 07:37.940
<b>based on what we've seen, 
and circumstantial evidence?</b>

07:38.560 --> 07:41.600
<b>I am certain that both killings 
were the work of a replicant.</b>

07:43.250 --> 07:45.590
<b>Did you report this to Police Chief Grant?</b>

07:48.220 --> 07:50.070
<b>He didn't believe me.</b>

07:56.390 --> 07:59.080
<b>Davis. What can I do for you?</b>

07:59.550 --> 08:03.460
<b><i>Chief, um, I finished my reports</i></b>

08:03.460 --> 08:05.250
<b>from the boxing club with forensic data,</b>

08:05.250 --> 08:08.140
<b>along with eyewitness accounts
of the female suspect.</b>

08:08.140 --> 08:08.830
<b>But--</b>

08:08.830 --> 08:12.200
<b>But what?</b>

08:12.590 --> 08:13.840
<b>Davis?</b>

08:14.810 --> 08:16.030
<b>Spit it out.</b>

08:17.720 --> 08:21.830
<b><i>Senator Bannister's neck was already 
broken before he hit the ground.</i></b>

08:22.090 --> 08:24.990
<b>This is superhuman strength.
Not the work of just any woman.</b>

08:24.990 --> 08:26.600
<b>I feel certain...</b>

08:30.620 --> 08:32.190
<b><i>She's a replicant.</i></b>

08:35.120 --> 08:36.920
<b>Well, well.</b>

08:38.390 --> 08:40.860
<b>You have quite the imagination.</b>

08:40.860 --> 08:44.130
<b>No, not really.
Sir, it adds up. I'll show you.</b>

08:58.300 --> 08:59.590
<b>Chief Grant.</b>

09:02.240 --> 09:05.800
<b>You didn't make it in the 
Blade Runner program, did you?</b>

09:07.520 --> 09:11.700
<b>There's no work for Blade Runners in this town.</b>

09:11.700 --> 09:14.030
<b>There just aren't any replicants left.</b>

09:14.030 --> 09:16.850
<b>But I saw the suspect myself, sir.</b>

09:19.340 --> 09:21.620
<b>And she has this tattoo.</b>

09:25.540 --> 09:28.740
<b>And you think it's a Replicant?
It's organized crime.</b>

09:28.740 --> 09:29.960
<b>Senator must've had enemies.</b>

09:29.960 --> 09:30.980
<b>But sir.</b>

09:32.530 --> 09:36.550
<b>my intuition... says I'm on the right track.</b>

09:36.550 --> 09:39.260
<b>Stop! That's enough.</b>

09:46.010 --> 09:48.330
<b>Drop it already, rookie.</b>

09:51.760 --> 09:52.730
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

09:55.270 --> 09:56.990
<b>You can leave that here.</b>

10:02.310 --> 10:04.800
<b>You were in the Blade Runner program?</b>

10:06.440 --> 10:07.960
<b>Well, nothing to be ashamed of.</b>

10:09.790 --> 10:12.340
<b>Even taking the test is an honor.</b>

10:12.340 --> 10:15.670
<b>First day failure rate is 
supposed to be around 95%</b>

10:15.670 --> 10:17.460
<b>99.4, actually.</b>

10:19.020 --> 10:20.590
<b>Why didn't you make it?</b>

10:21.270 --> 10:23.420
<b>Same as everyone else.</b>

10:23.950 --> 10:25.450
<b>My intuition.</b>

10:26.700 --> 10:28.840
<b>So you talked to Chief Grant.</b>

10:28.840 --> 10:30.180
<b>Then what happened?</b>

10:31.330 --> 10:33.130
<b>I was taken off the case.</b>

10:34.870 --> 10:38.910
<b>Then he mobilized the entire force to sweep 
the city and flush Black Lotus out.</b>

10:40.080 --> 10:41.640
<b>Hold it right there!</b>

10:44.350 --> 10:45.670
<b>Give it a rest!</b>

10:47.110 --> 10:49.570
<b>Black Lotus tattoo.
You seen her?</b>

10:53.860 --> 10:55.540
<b>But there was no trace of her.</b>

10:56.840 --> 10:59.400
<b>That was the night Chief Grant Died.</b>

11:00.430 --> 11:02.070
<b>And you were there.</b>

11:03.880 --> 11:05.460
<b>I arrived just after.</b>

11:05.460 --> 11:08.100
<b>Even though you said yourself 
you were off the case.</b>

11:08.650 --> 11:10.060
<b>You were angry at him.</b>

11:10.360 --> 11:12.530
<b>It was my investigation.</b>

11:12.530 --> 11:15.890
<b>I did the legwork.
I identified the suspect.</b>

11:15.890 --> 11:17.780
<b>I did everything right.</b>

11:18.400 --> 11:20.030
<b>So why am I a suspect?</b>

11:23.670 --> 11:26.690
<b>Black Lotus shows up somewhere, and so do you.</b>

11:26.920 --> 11:29.110
<b>That doesn't seem like just a coincidence to me.</b>

11:30.370 --> 11:34.330
<b>I think you're somehow involved 
with Chief Grant's murder.</b>

11:34.330 --> 11:36.710
<b>Your career is off to a promising start.</b>

11:37.360 --> 11:39.650
<b>But there are a thousand ways it could end.</b>

11:40.770 --> 11:42.500
<b>What do you want from me?</b>

11:42.790 --> 11:44.490
<b>The truth about what you know.</b>

11:45.610 --> 11:48.130
<b>And if I don't like the answers you give me</b>

11:48.130 --> 11:50.270
<b>or I find out you're lying to me? 
I throw the book at you.</b>

11:50.650 --> 11:54.040
<b>You can't threaten me.
I've done nothing wrong.</b>

11:54.600 --> 11:57.100
<b>Why don't you let me be the judge of that?</b>

12:04.710 --> 12:05.920
<b>Please.</b>

12:06.850 --> 12:09.420
<b>Tell me everything that happened that night.</b>

12:10.890 --> 12:13.920
<b>Chief took over the 
Black Lotus investigation.</b>

12:14.410 --> 12:16.370
<b>That seemed suspicious to me.</b>

12:19.940 --> 12:23.340
<b>Then I saw him leaving in a hurry</b>

12:23.830 --> 12:26.100
<b>when we're supposed to 
be hunting Black Lotus.</b>

12:33.290 --> 12:34.600
<b>Hey, Chief.</b>

12:35.010 --> 12:38.510
<b>And the longer I looked, 
the more suspicious he seemed.</b>

12:38.510 --> 12:41.240
<b>So I followed him back to his house.</b>

12:47.650 --> 12:48.540
<b>Freeze!</b>

12:48.770 --> 12:52.840
<b>That's when I finally ran into her.
Face-to-face.</b>

12:53.930 --> 12:55.540
<b>Black Lotus.</b>

12:57.200 --> 12:59.850
<b>Put the sword down.</b>

13:21.640 --> 13:23.680
<b>Police!
Drop your weapon!</b>

13:24.580 --> 13:27.300
<b>I'm a Blade Runner. She's mine.</b>

13:30.270 --> 13:32.260
<b>Before he'd been killed,</b>

13:32.260 --> 13:34.600
<b>records show Chief Grant had 
called in a Blade Runner.</b>

13:45.390 --> 13:49.720
<b>An ordinary replicant would have no 
chance against a Blade Runner.</b>

14:01.280 --> 14:05.240
<b>But Black Lotus is no ordinary replicant.</b>

14:27.710 --> 14:30.980
<b>I saw it with my own eyes.</b>

14:32.620 --> 14:36.100
<b>When I told Chief she was a 
replicant, he re-assigned me.</b>

14:38.140 --> 14:39.320
<b>No!</b>

14:49.850 --> 14:52.670
<b>Then he went and brought in a Blade Runner?</b>

14:53.260 --> 14:55.480
<b>Grant lied to you.</b>

14:55.480 --> 14:57.480
<b>Or he was hiding something.</b>

14:58.160 --> 15:02.250
<b>And now, I can't even ask him about it.</b>

15:09.950 --> 15:11.800
<b>Let's say you're right.</b>

15:12.170 --> 15:15.050
<b>Grant knew that Black Lotus is a replicant.</b>

15:15.650 --> 15:17.870
<b>Why would he try to cover it up?</b>

15:19.660 --> 15:20.950
<b>I don't know.</b>

15:22.570 --> 15:28.060
<b>NEXUS 8 model replicants have learned 
to stay alive by keeping a low profile.</b>

15:28.700 --> 15:31.950
<b>But Black Lotus is making a lot of waves,</b>

15:31.950 --> 15:33.810
<b>and wasn't afraid of a Blade Runner.</b>

15:34.460 --> 15:39.610
<b>She can't be a NEXUS 8, 
and replicant production was banned in 2023.</b>

15:39.610 --> 15:40.760
<b>But what if--</b>

15:41.970 --> 15:45.450
<b>what if someone's making new ones?</b>

15:47.770 --> 15:50.000
<b>You almost had me going there.</b>

15:48.720 --> 15:50.000
<b>Let me finish.</b>

15:50.000 --> 15:50.660
<b>No.</b>

15:50.660 --> 15:53.390
<b>This is entertaining, 
but you have no evidence.</b>

15:55.470 --> 15:59.150
<b>There's more.
What Black Lotus told me.</b>

15:59.770 --> 16:01.490
<b>And what's that?</b>

16:04.370 --> 16:07.380
<b>I'm done being hunted like an animal.</b>

16:10.550 --> 16:13.840
<b>You don't want to be hunted, 
maybe you shouldn't be killing people.</b>

16:19.200 --> 16:21.120
<b>I'm not the one who started this.</b>

16:22.400 --> 16:24.270
<b>What are you talking about?</b>

16:25.660 --> 16:27.790
<b>These weren't random killings.</b>

16:27.790 --> 16:30.240
<b>She targeted them for a reason.</b>

16:30.720 --> 16:34.040
<b>And from the sound of her voice, 
it was personal.</b>

16:37.080 --> 16:40.010
<b>I went back to review the 
whole case from the beginning</b>

16:40.970 --> 16:44.330
<b>starting with the Senator's 
journalist friend, Hooper.</b>

16:44.330 --> 16:47.790
<b>Before Hooper disappeared, 
he chartered a plane.</b>

16:48.270 --> 16:50.580
<b>Not a trace of her...</b>

16:50.870 --> 16:52.910
<b>The trip plans had been altered,</b>

16:52.910 --> 16:55.190
<b>but I found the flight record coordinates</b>

16:55.820 --> 16:59.250
<b>putting him in the Nevada desert.</b>

16:59.920 --> 17:02.000
<b>Desert's off-limits.</b>

17:03.910 --> 17:05.960
<b>Unless you have connections.</b>

17:05.960 --> 17:11.500
<b>Chief Grant and his wife took their 
vacation on the same day as Hooper.</b>

17:12.190 --> 17:15.390
<b>I'll bet Senator Bannister 
had the same time off.</b>

17:15.790 --> 17:16.830
<b>Okay.</b>

17:19.350 --> 17:23.920
<b>If you know where to look, 
maybe I can help you find some answers.</b>

18:04.730 --> 18:07.190
<b>What the hell happened out here?</b>

18:46.000 --> 18:48.090
<b>I called in a dig team.</b>

18:48.090 --> 18:49.350
<b>They'll pull the bodies.</b>

18:49.350 --> 18:50.670
<b>Try to ID them.</b>

18:57.800 --> 19:00.590
<b>Wouldn't be surprised if 
they find Hooper out there.</b>

19:02.330 --> 19:05.540
<b>This isn't about finding a 
killer replicant anymore.</b>

19:06.630 --> 19:08.370
<b>You believe me now?</b>

19:13.240 --> 19:15.480
<b>You've uncovered something big here, Davis.</b>

19:15.980 --> 19:17.970
<b>I'll report this to my superiors.</b>

19:19.370 --> 19:21.510
<b>This is going to be a big deal for you.</b>

20:08.510 --> 20:09.950
<b>Officer Davis,</b>

20:10.480 --> 20:14.210
<b>based on the recommendations of the 
investigation, you have been diagnosed</b>

20:14.210 --> 20:19.070
<b>with delusional tendencies that interfere 
with your duties as a police officer.</b>

20:19.640 --> 20:24.280
<b>As of this moment, you are on leave 
for no less than three months.</b>

20:24.280 --> 20:29.150
<b><i>Go home and come to terms 
with your condition.</i></b>

20:44.470 --> 20:49.020
<b><i>Tyrell Corporation proprietary intellectual 
rights rumored to be available</i></b>

20:49.020 --> 20:54.320
<b><i>for an undisclosed sum by 
the Wallace Corporation.</i></b>

20:57.430 --> 21:01.020
<b><i>I'd trust a silent robber</i></b>

21:01.020 --> 21:04.380
<b><i>More than I would trust 
you coming through my door</i></b>

21:12.540 --> 21:14.250
<b><i>It's all connected.</i></b>

21:13.490 --> 21:16.740
<b><i>I only listen to my intuition</i></b>

21:16.740 --> 21:19.780
<b><i>She's the only one who tells me the truth</i></b>

21:19.330 --> 21:22.070
<b><i>I'm gonna find Black Lotus.</i></b>

