<b><i>And she tells me that she doesn't like you</i></b>

21:44.210 --> 21:48.340
<b><i>If she's going down, it's all alone</i></b>

21:48.340 --> 21:52.040
<b><i>I won't be around to see the swoop</i></b>

21:52.040 --> 21:54.640
<b><i>Your words fall to the ground</i></b>

